        Changelog
        =========
        
        1.2.0 - Released 2009-10-21
        ----------------
        
        * Force HTTPS in sending login credentials [ekantola]
        * Removed breadcrumbs and portlet admin links from print media (CSS) [ekantola]
        * Added WebDAV support (/dav) [ekantola]
        * Fixed image layout setting so that now it actually does something [ekantola]
        * Fixed calendar portlet title and dates [pkantola]
        * Always show the right portlet area [pkantola]
        * Fixed the Ploneboard newest conversations portlet [pkantola]
        
        1.1.6 - Released 2009-08-16
        ----------------
        
        * Improved calendar with better year navigation
        
        1.1.5 - Released 2009-06-16
        ----------------
        
        * Removed the customized contact-info.cpt to fix the broken contact
          info form
        
        1.1.4 - Released 2009-05-28
        ----------------
        
        * Reverted search.pt because some recent changes broke it
        
        1.1.3 - Released 2009-05-25
        ----------------
        
        * Calendar view now displays all the months of visible years even if
          the months contain no events - ekantola
        
        1.1.2 - Released 2009-05-24
        ----------------
        
        * Much improved folder calendar view
        
        1.1.1 - Released 2009-05-21
        ----------------
        
        * Small MyLogin portlet fixes
        
        1.1 - Unreleased
        ----------------
        
        * MyLogin portlet
        
        0.1 - Unreleased
        ----------------
        
        * Initial release
        
        
